      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WESTERN LIES (8) goes very well here starting 10 times for six wins and two minors. Scored by 4.5 lengths last time (23.28) in a NG over 411m at Casino. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. FEDERAL PLAYER (3) is a talented type who boasts a strong winning strike-rate at this distance. Has quickly put himself into the picture to win the last couple of runs. Last start won Maitland in a handy 22.02 beating Freight Express. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Sure to be thereabouts. FEDERAL SENOR (4) was a last start winner (22.02) at Gosford who is building a strong winning record. Has an impeccable record at this journey winning all six. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Hard to fault the current string of winning form and can continue his winning ways. WAGTAIL WHISPER (1) is always a threat when he races at this journey.",
